" end="00:13.840" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:11.072" end="00:11.369">We</span> <span begin="00:11.369" end="00:11.607">have</span> <span begin="00:11.607" end="00:11.756">the</span> <span begin="00:11.756" end="00:12.006">check</span> <span begin="00:12.006" end="00:12.625">stubs</span> <span begin="00:12.625" end="00:12.803">from</span> <span begin="00:12.803" end="00:13.226">separate</span> <span begin="00:13.226" end="00:13.840">accounts</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们拿到了来自不同账户的支票存根</span></p><p begin="00:13.956" end="00:16.555" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:13.956" end="00:14.276">Almost</span> <span begin="00:14.276" end="00:14.444">a</span> <span begin="00:14.444" end="00:14.775">thousand</span> <span begin="00:14.775" end="00:15.143">dollars</span> <span begin="00:15.143" end="00:15.359">paid</span> <span begin="00:15.359" end="00:15.511">in</span> <span begin="00:15.511" end="00:15.860">different</span> <span begin="00:15.860" end="00:16.555">amounts</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">总额将近一千美元，分多次支付</span></p><p begin="00:16.591" end="00:19.973" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:16.591" end="00:16.852">To</span> <span begin="00:16.852" end="00:17.022">a</span> <span begin="00:17.022" end="00:17.353">Mr.</span> <span begin="00:17.353" end="00:17.636">James</span> <span begin="00:17.636" end="00:18.169">Reynolds</span> <span begin="00:18.169" end="00:18.353">way</span> <span begin="00:18.353" end="00:18.569">back</span> <span begin="00:18.569" end="00:18.740">in</span> <span begin="00:18.740" end="00:19.973">1791</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">支付给一位詹姆斯·雷诺兹先生，早在 1791 年就开始了</span></p><p begin="00:19.973" end="00:22.256" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:19.973" end="00:20.245">Is</span> <span begin="00:20.245" end="00:20.512">that</span> <span begin="00:20.512" end="00:20.728">what</span> <span begin="00:20.728" end="00:20.962">you</s