rom</span> <span begin="00:29.642" end="00:29.789">your</span> <span begin="00:29.789" end="00:30.231">sacred</span> <span begin="00:30.231" end="00:30.573">nation</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你背离了神圣的国家，去谋取经济利益</span></p><p begin="00:30.657" end="00:33.723" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:30.657" end="00:30.830">And</span> <span begin="00:30.830" end="00:30.984">the</span> <span begin="00:30.984" end="00:31.481">evidence</span> <span begin="00:31.481" end="00:31.930">suggests</span> <span begin="00:31.930" end="00:32.037">you</span> <span begin="00:32.037" end="00:32.364">engaged</span> <span begin="00:32.364" end="00:32.478">in</span> <span begin="00:32.478" end="00:33.723">speculation</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">证据表明你参与了（公款）投机</span></p><p begin="00:33.472" end="00:36.357" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:33.472" end="00:33.633">An</span> <span begin="00:33.633" end="00:34.186">immigrant</span> <span begin="00:34.186" end="00:34.852">embezzling</span> <span begin="00:34.852" end="00:35.031">our</span> <span begin="00:35.031" end="00:35.649">government</span> <span begin="00:35.649" end="00:36.357">funds</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一个移民贪污我们的政府资金</span></p><p begin="00:36.064" end="00:39.072" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:36.064" end="00:36.245">I</span> <span begin="00:36.245" end="00:36.429">can</span> <span begin="00:36.429" end="00:36.754">almost</span> <span begin="00:36.754" end="00:36.914">see</span> <span begin="00:36.914" end="00:37.098">the</span> <span begin="00:37.098" end="00:37.424">headline,</span> <span begin="00:37.424" end="00:37.690">your</span> <span begin="00:37.690" end="00:38.138">career</span> <span begin="00:38.138" end="00:38.472">is</span> <span begin="00:38.472" end="00:39.072">done</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我几乎能预见到头条新闻了，你的职业生涯完蛋了</span></p><p begin="00:38.864" end="00:41.805" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="00:38.864" end="00:39.050">I</span> <span begin="00:39.050" end="00:39.367">hope</span> <span begin="00:39.367" end="00:39.535">you</span> <span begin="00:39.535" end="00:39.749">saved</span> <span begin="00:39.749" end="00:39.950">some</span> <span begin="00:39.950" end="00:40.255">money</span> <span begin="00:40.255" end="00:40.368">for</span> <span begin="00:40.368" end="00:40.546">your</span> <span begin="00:40.546" end="00:40.927">daughter</span> <span begin="00:40.927" end="00:41.165">and</span> <span begin="00:41.165" end="00:41.805">son</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我希望你给你的儿女攒了点钱</span></p><p begin="00:41.805" end="00:44.891" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="00:41.805" end="00:41.995">Ya</span> <span begin="00:41.995" end="00:42.352">best</span> <span begin="00:42.352" end="00:42.727">g'wan</span> <span begin="00:42.727" end="00:43.072">run</span> <span begin="00:43.072" end="00:43.417">back</span> <span begin="00:43.417" end="00:43.626">where</span> <span begin="00:43.626" end="00:43.875">ya</span> <span begin="00:43.875" end="00:44.274">come</span> <span begin="00:44.274" end="00:44.891">from!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你最好赶紧滚回你原来的地方去！</span></p><p begin="00:45.340" end="00:50.656" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="00:45.340" end="00:46.058">Ha!</span> <span begin="00:46.286" end="00:46.411">You</span> <span begin="00:46.411" end="00:46.655">don't</span> <span begin="00:46.655" end="00:46.982">even</span> <span begin="00:46.982" end="00:47.369">know</span> <span begin="00:47.369" end="00:47.577">what</span> <span begin="00:47.577" end="00:47.744">you're</span> <span begin="00:47.744" end="00:48.171">asking</span> <span begin="00:48.171" end="00:48.439">me</span> <span begin="00:48.439" end="00:48.618">to</span> <span begin="00:48.618" end="00:50.005">confess</span> <span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:49.398" end="00:50.656"><span begin="00:49.398" end="00:50.656">(Confess)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">交代吧</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">哈！你们甚至都不知道自己在要求我交代什么</span></p><p begin="00:50.656" end="00:56.307" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="00:50.656" end="00:50.870">You</span> <span begin="00:50.870" end="00:51.096">have</span> <span begin="00:51.096" end="00:51.519">nothing,</span> <span begin="00:51.519" end="00:51.644">I</span> <span begin="00:51.644" end="00:51.816">don't</span> <span begin="00:51.816" end="00:52.018">have</span> <span begin="00:52.018" end="00:52.173">to</span> <span begin="00:52.173" end="00:52.381">tell</span> <span begin="00:52.381" end="00:52.548">you</span> <span begin="00:52.548" end="00:53.071">anything</span> <span begin="00:53.071" end="00:53.262">at</span> <span begin="00:53.262" end="00:53.974">all,</span> <span begin="00:54.320" end="00:54.850">un</span><span begin="00:54.850" end="00:55.373">less</span> <span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="00:55.023" end="00:56.307"><span begin="00:55.023" end="00:55.665">(Un</span><span begin="00:55.665" end="00:56.307">less)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">除非……</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你们什么都没有，我根本不需要告诉你们任何事，除非……</span></p><p begin="00:56.039" end="00:58.372" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="00:56.039" end="00:56.348">If</span> <span begin="00:56.348" end="00:56.448">I</span> <span begin="00:56.448" end="00:56.604">can</span> <span begin="00:56.604" end="00:56.979">prove</span> <span begin="00:56.979" end="00:57.146">that</span> <span begin="00:57.146" end="00:57.259">I</span> <span begin="00:57.259" end="00:57.654">never</span> <span begin="00:57.654" end="00:57.860">broke</span> <span begin="00:57.860" end="00:58.038">the</span> <span begin="00:58.038" end="00:58.372">law</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果我能证明我从未触犯法律</span></p><p begin="00:58.372" end="01:01.605" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="00:58.372" end="00:58.545">Do</span> <span begin="00:58.545" end="00:58.741">you</span> <span begin="00:58.741" end="00:59.098">promise</span> <span begin="00:59.098" end="00:59.270">not</span> <span begin="00:59.270" end="00:59.431">to</span> <span begin="00:59.431" end="00:59.615">tell</span> <span begin="00:59.615" end="00:59.984">another</span> <span begin="00:59.984" end="01:00.544">soul</span> <span begin="01:00.544" end="01:00.746">what</span> <span begin="01:00.746" end="01:00.978">you</span> <span begin="01:00.978" end="01:01.605">saw?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你们能保证不把所见所闻告诉任何一个人吗？</span></p><p begin="01:01.857" end="01:04.456" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:01.857" end="01:02.073">No</span> <span begin="01:02.073" end="01:02.273">one</span> <span begin="01:02.273" end="01:02.470">else</span> <span begin="01:02.470" end="01:02.643">was</span> <span begin="01:02.643" end="01:02.809">in</span> <span begin="01:02.809" end="01:03.022">the</span> <span begin="01:03.022" end="01:03.428">room</span> <span begin="01:03.428" end="01:03.660">where</span> <span begin="01:03.660" end="01:03.760">it</span> <span begin="01:03.760" end="01:04.456">happened</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">没人在那个事发的房间里</span></p><p begin="01:04.456" end="01:05.589" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="01:04.456" end="01:04.652">Is</span> <span begin="01:04.652" end="01:04.789">that</span> <span begin="01:04.789" end="01:04.991">a</span> <span begin="01:04.991" end="01:05.589">yes?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这算答应了吗？</span></p><p begin="01:06.072" end="01:07.389" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="01:06.072" end="01:06.816">Um,</span> <span begin="01:06.816" end="01:07.389">yes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">额，好吧</span></p><p begin="01:09.540" end="01:12.539" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="01:09.540" end="01:09.871">"Dear</span> <span begi